===評價===
《全面進化》獲得了大多混合性和負面的評價，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上45家媒体综评42分，[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]新鲜度只有19%。評論家认为影片的邏輯和故事線比较贫瘠<ref>{{cite news | last=Ryan | first=Tim | url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/04/18/review-revue-transcendence-heaven-is-for-real-bears-a-haunted-house-2/ | title=Review Revue: 'Transcendence,' 'Heaven Is for Real,' 'Bears,' 'A Haunted House 2' | work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] | date=April 18, 2014 | accessdate=April 19, 2014 | archive-date=2014-04-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420124855/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/04/18/review-revue-transcendence-heaven-is-for-real-bears-a-haunted-house-2/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last=Gettell | first=Oliver | url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-transcendence-johnny-depp-movie-reviews-critics-20140418,0,1613607.story | title='Transcendence': Techno-thriller doesn't compute, critics say | work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | date=April 18, 2014 | accessdate=April 18, 2014 | archive-date=2014-04-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426150023/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-transcendence-johnny-depp-movie-reviews-critics-20140418,0,1613607.story | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

美媒认为：“从头到尾都是瞎扯，犹如一场毫无意义的噩梦，没有丝毫情节！剧情犹如碎片四处飘散”，“片中有大量的[[人工智能|人工智能]]理论，但讽刺性在于，整部影片没有半点智能之处”，“影片没有反角、没有刺激点，更没有高潮点，除了诺兰粉丝的捧场外，我看不出有谁会有兴趣来观看本片”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/hlw/2014-04-21/18274130419_2.shtml |title=本周新片：《天堂为真》《鬼屋大电影2》 |accessdate=2014-05-01 |archive-date=2014-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425160014/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/hlw/2014-04-21/18274130419_2.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

被《[[时代杂志|时代杂志]]》评为年度十大差片第九名。<ref >{{cite web |url=http://news.mtime.com/2014/12/04/1534808.html |language= |title=美国"时代"杂志年度十佳电影出炉 |publisher=时光网 |date=2014-12-04 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213023547/http://news.mtime.com/2014/12/04/1534808.html |archive-date=2014-12-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

